Package: variogramApp
Type: Package
Title: Shiny application for illustrating variogram
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Olatunji Johnson [cre, aut] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4080-0999>)
Maintainer: Olatunji Johnson <olatunjijohnson21111@gmail.com>
Description: The variogramApp package runs a Shiny web application that allows for
    explore variogram by varying its parameters. It also allows user to visualise the
    reaisation of its corresponding Gaussian process.
Imports: geoR, ggplot2, shiny, dplyr
